{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:21:49.744Z","taskId":"KB-003","text":"or that it doesn't — establishing the boundary between store and engine responsibility).\n\n### Suggestions\n\n- Consider adding a `resetPlayback()` internal helper or having `nextTrack`/`prevTrack` also set `isPlaying` to `false` so the audio engine can decide to auto-play. Currently `nextTrack` and `prevTrack` don't touch `isPlaying`, which means the engine (Step 3) must","type":"text","agent":"reviewer"}
