{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:23:46.025Z","taskId":"KB-003","text":"### Issues Found\n\n1. **[Severity: important]** — **Missing `playbackState = 'loading'` at start of `load()`**. The plan specifies that `on('load')` sets `playbackState` to `'paused'` and `on('loaderror')` sets it to `'error'`, but never explicitly says to set `playbackState` to `'loading'` at the","type":"text","agent":"reviewer"}
