{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:58.427Z","taskId":"KB-003","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the implementation. Let me assess the Step 7 changes specifically:\n\n## Code Review: Step 7 — Astro Integration — ViewTransitions and Layout Mount\n\n### Verdict: APPROVE\n\n### Summary\nThe Step 7 implementation correctly integrates the Player component into `BaseLayout.astro` with ViewTransitions support, `transition:persist` for DOM persistence across navigations,","type":"text","agent":"reviewer"}
